(11, 'Staghorn Fern', '4', '<b>Staghorn Fern </b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p> Also Known as Platycerium, elkhorn ferns, have an out-of-this world appearance. The plants have two types of leaves, one of which resembles the horns of a large herbivore.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Plant Size </b>: 0.5-3 feet\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs.  604', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/1-Staghorn-Fern.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Decoretive-Plants/c/12867098/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 5, 2, 1, ''),
(12, 'Polynesian stand', '4', '<b> Polynesian stand</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>A beautiful ginger plant with attractive foliage producing plastic orange cone-shaped terminal flowers.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Plant size</b> : 2-6 feet\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : 1200', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/2-polynesian-stand1.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Decoretive-Plants/c/12867098/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 4, 2, 1, ''),
(13, 'Purple-Shamrock', '4', '<b>Purple shamrock</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Oxalis triangularis, commonly called False Shamrock, is a species of edible perennial plant in the Oxalidaceae family. It is endemic to Brazil.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Plant Size</b> : 0.5-3 feet\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> :  Rs.  484', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/3-purple-shamrock.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Decoretive-Plants/c/12867098/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 3, 2, 1, ''),
(14, 'Crassula Campfire', '4', '<b>Crassula Campfire</b> \r\n<br><br>\r\n<p> Crassula Campfire is an Easy-to-grow, branching succulent that displays dramatic, fleshy, propeller-like leaves that mature from light green to bright red.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Plant Size</b> : 0.5-3 feet\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b>:    R 229', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/4-Crassula-Campfire2.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Decoretive-Plants/c/12867098/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 2, 2, 1, ''),
(15, 'Euphorbia (Red Mini)', '4', '<b>Euphorbia (Red Mini)</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>The Euphorbia milii plant is a beautiful plant that will brighten up your home or landscape. It is easy to grow and will provide blooms that last a long time.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Plant Size</b> : 0.5-3 feet\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b>:    R 425 ', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/5-euphorbia-red-mini-1.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Decoretive-Plants/c/12867098/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 1, 2, 1, ''),
(16, 'Ficus', '4', '<b>Ficus</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p> The Ficus also known as the weeping tree is a beautiful evergreen plant.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Plant Size</b> : 0.5-3 feet\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b>: Rs. 1375', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/6-Ficus.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Decoretive-Plants/c/12867098/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 0, 2, 1, ''),
(34, 'Glows', '9', '<b>Glows</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Gardening glows is made for use when keep gardening in ome made garden nursery.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : <b>400</b> gm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 550 \r\n', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/1.Glows_.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Farming-Tools/c/12867070/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 8, 2, 1, ''),
(17, 'Small Bamboo plant', '5', '<b>Small Bamboo plant</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Lucky bamboo is not bamboo at all, but a species called Dracaena sanderiana.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\nPlant Size : 0.5-3 feet\r\n<br><br>\r\nPrice:    Rs: 357', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/1-amall-bamboo-plant.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Gift-Plants/c/12867100/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 5, 2, 1, ''),
(18, 'Straight Sticks', '5', '<b>Straight Sticks</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Straight Sticks Lucky bamboo plants make perfect gifts for any occasion and can symbolize ingredients to a happy life.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Plant Size</b> : 0.5-3 feet\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 500', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/2-Straight-Sticks1.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Gift-Plants/c/12867100/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 4, 2, 1, ''),
(19, 'Adenium-red', '5', '<b>Adenium-red</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Adenium is an excellent plant that thrives without much attention. \r\nThe plant is a spreading succulent bush, two metres in fleshy, may be rigid and upright, with rather weak and spreading, short branches.\r\nAlso known as the desert rose.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Plant size</b> : 0.5-3 feet\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs.  850', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/3-adenium-red.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Gift-Plants/c/12867100/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 3, 2, 1, ''),
(23, 'Small White pebbs', '6', '<b>Small White pebbs</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>500gm</b> of pebbles,\r\n<br><br> \r\n<b>Size</b> : medium \r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Texture</b> : solid \r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Color</b> : natural white\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b>  :  Rs. 100  per 500 gm', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/2-small-white-pebbs.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Pebbes/c/12867078/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 4, 2, 1, ''),
(20, 'Pachira plant', '5', '<b>Pachira plant</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Pachiras are relative of the baobab trees and both are the members of bombacaceae family.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Plant size</b> : 0.5-3 feet\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> :  Rs. 550 ', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/4-pachira-plant2.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Gift-Plants/c/12867100/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 2, 2, 1, ''),
(21, 'Gold Fish plant', '5', '<b>Gold Fish plant</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Goldfish plants come to us from the Central and South American tropics from the unusual shape of their flowers which, with some imagination, resemble fish.\r\nbr><br>\r\n<b>Plant size</b> : 3 - 4 feet\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs.  1200  ', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/5-gold-fish-plant.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Gift-Plants/c/12867100/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 1, 2, 1, ''),
(22, 'Adenium-obesum plant', '5', '<b>Adenium-obesum</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Through out the year blooming plant, can be used in pot on roof top area. Also known as the desert rose.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Plant Size</b> : 0.5-3 feet\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Thumbnail on left shows actual image. \r\nAcutal plant may vary in height.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b>:   Rs. 950', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/6-adenium-obesum-.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Gift-Plants/c/12867100/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 0, 2, 1, ''),
(24, 'Aquariam pebbs', '6', '<b>Aquariam pebbs</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>500gm</b> of pebbles\r\n<br><br> \r\n<b>Size</b> : medium \r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Texture</b> : solid\r\n<br><br> \r\n<b>Color</b> : blue raspberry\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : 200 rs per 500 gm', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/aquariam-pebbs.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Pebbes/c/12867078/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 3, 2, 1, ''),
(25, 'Granite pebbs', '6', '<b>Granite pebbes</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>500gm</b> of pebbles\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Size</b> : medium\r\n<br><br> \r\n<b>Texture</b> : granite\r\n<br><br> \r\n<b>Color</b> : shadow white\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : 150 rs per 500 gm', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/granite-pebbs.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Pebbes/c/12867078/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 2, 2, 1, ''),
(26, 'Onex simple pebbs', '6', '<b>Onex simple pebbs</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>500gm</b> of pebbles \r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Size</b> : medium \r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Texture</b> : onex simple \r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Color</b> : mix colores\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : 200 rs per 500 gm', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/onex-pebs.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Pebbes/c/12867078/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 1, 2, 1, ''),
(27, 'Mix-Black pebbs', '6', '<b>Mix-Black pebbs</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>500gm</b> of pebbles \r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Size</b> : medium\r\n<br><br> \r\n<b>Texture</b> : marble\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Color</b> : super white\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : 100 rs per 500 gm', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/small-mix-pebbs.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Pebbes/c/12867078/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 0, 2, 1, ''),
(28, 'Summer flower seeds', '7', '<b>Summer flower seeds</b>\r\n<br><br> \r\n<p>Specially for summer season flower seeds. Its like a desert rose. very colorful flowers can grow up with care of regular tritment.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b>  :  250 gm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b>  : Rs 725 per 250 gm package', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/1-summer-flower-seeds.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Seeds/c/12867083/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 4, 2, 1, ''),
(29, 'Unique rose seeds', '7', '<b>Unique rose seeds</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>The pack containing 250 gm packets of Rose Seeds. Very colorful flowers of rose can grow up with care of regular tritment.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b>  : 250 gm\r\n<br><br> \r\n<b>Price</b>  :  Rs.  850 per 250 gm packaeges', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/2-unique-rose.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Seeds/c/12867083/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 3, 2, 1, ''),
(30, 'Winter flower seeds', '7', '<b>Winter flower seeds</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Give your birb a wintry look with Winter Flower Plant Packs. Perfect with Winter Flower Plant Packs and/or Autumn Fern Plant Packs.</p>\r\n<br><br> \r\n<b>Weight</b>  : 250 gm \r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs.  575 per 250 gm packages', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/3-winter-flower.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Seeds/c/12867083/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 2, 2, 1, ''),
(31, 'Forever vincase seeds', '7', '<b>Forever vincase seeds</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Vinca stands up to heat, humidity, and rain beautifully, and blooms heavily all summer. It does not need either deadheading or pinching to maintain its bloom and form and is highly resistant to Deer and Disease.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b>  : 250 gm\r\n<br><br> \r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs.  450 per 250 gm package', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/4-forever-vincase.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Seeds/c/12867083/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 1, 2, 1, ''),
(32, 'Rainy flower seeds', '7', '<b>Rainy flower seeds</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Provide plenty of moisture during our drought season. Slugs are a problem with young plants. Easily started from seed.\r\nGood hummingbird, butterfly and bee plant.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b>  :  250 gm \r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b>  : Rs.  675 per 250 gm packages', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/5-rainy-flower.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Seeds/c/12867083/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 0, 2, 1, ''),
(33, 'Aglaonema plant', '8', '<b>Aglaonema (Chinese Evergreen)</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Aglaonema plant is an indoor decorative and also foliage plant. It belongs from Araceae family and it is known as Chinese evergreen as its common name. Its scientific name is Aglaonema modestum and Aglaonema commutatum. It has green stem and large leaves; it does not blooms flowers. Aglaonema plant needs sunlight and moist weather for plant growing. But direct sunlight can be damaged this plants growing and it can grow under shade. Regular watering must be need in summer, but in winter it needs quite water for its growth as well as drying is harmful for this plant growth. Temperature must be over 15C and cold weather can spoil this plant growth, because it needs warm weather. Fertilizing like liquid fertilizer needed for Aglaonema plant growth.</p>', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Aglaonema-Emerald-Bay-1.jpg;http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/tumblr_mxn7yzIIX41qjwd8go1_5001.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=417&group_id=7', '', 'on', 0, 2, 1, ''),
(69, 'Marigold-Yellow-African', '14', '<b>Marigold-yellow-african</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Season time</b> : Spring\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>This plant was used in ancient Greek, Roman, Arabic and Indian cultures as a medicinal herb as well as a dye for fabrics, foods and cosmetics. The leaves are edible, with the petals added to dishes as a garnish and in lieu of saffron.<p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Height<b> : 3.5 to 5.0 ft\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price<b> : Rs. 225', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/1.marigold-yellow-african.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Seasonal-Plants/c/12867096/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 5, 2, 1, ''),
(35, 'Planting-Hole', '9', '<br>Planting-Hole</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>A landscape designer''s favorite! There are so many uses for this Japanese-made tool but our favorite is for planting bulbs! This tool is used to make trenches for planing seeds and replanting bedding plants.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 1250 gm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 450 ', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/2.Planting-Hole.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Farming-Tools/c/12867070/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 7, 2, 1, ''),
(36, 'Felco-cutter', '9', '<b>Felco-cutter</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Good choice of pruners for those wishing to avoid tendonitis from prolonged and heavy pruning. Single-handed pruning shear has an extra-long cutting blade handle that allows the use of both hands when cutting extra thick branches. </p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Length</b> : 10.5" inch\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 750 gm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 750\r\n', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/3.felco-cutter.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Farming-Tools/c/12867070/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 6, 2, 1, ''),
(37, 'Coke-small', '9', '<b>Coke-small</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n <p>This high quality, Japanese made tool was originally designed for trimming sheep. It has many uses such as hedging, harvesting lettuce, and topping off garlic & onions before flowering. </p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Length</b> : 12" inch\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 350 gm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 475', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/4.coke-small.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Farming-Tools/c/12867070/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 5, 2, 1, ''),
(38, 'Graft-cutter', '9', '<b>Graft-cutter</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Folding grafting knife features a hardwood handle and a locking device that will not let the blade slip shut while in use. </p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Length</b> : 4" inch\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 250 gm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> :Rs. 1250', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/5.graft-cutter.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Farming-Tools/c/12867070/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 4, 2, 1, ''),
(39, 'Power-gear', '9', '<b>Power-gear</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>As with all the PowerGear tools your cutting power is doubled with each stroke. Sharp precision 9in blades are made of hardened steel with a non-stick coating. Lightweight, durable Nyglass handles.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Length</b> : 15" inch\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 2.5 kg\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 1500', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/6.Power-gear.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Farming-Tools/c/12867070/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 3, 2, 1, ''),
(40, 'Spred-Ferti', '9', '<b>Spred-Ferti</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Spread plastic tank of fertilizer.Powered by a 12-volt lead-gel battery that can be recharged in approximately five hours, this Solo 5 gallon backpack sprayer eliminates the pumping hassles of typical backpack sprayers and the emissions from motorized models.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Weight</p> : 5.5 kg\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Water-bearing capicity</b> : 20 liter\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>price</b> : Rs. 2500', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/7.Spred-Ferti.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Farming-Tools/c/12867070/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 2, 2, 1, ''),
(41, 'Loan-mover', '9', '<b>Loan-mover</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Small electric loan remover machine for home made garden or nursery.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 6 kg\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 2000', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/8.Loan-mover.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Farming-Tools/c/12867070/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 1, 2, 1, ''),
(42, 'Diging-showel', '9', '<b>Diging-showel</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>All steel construction for heavy-duty digging and durability; pre-sharpened, ready to use blade.Big step for foot security.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Length</b> : 3.5 feet\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 2.5 kg\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 1250', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/9.Diging-showel.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Farming-Tools/c/12867070/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 0, 2, 1, ''),
(43, 'Black-round', '10', '<b>Black-round</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Round pots, Comfortable for 3 small plant''s.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Size</b> : "5 X 5" inch.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 250 gm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 125', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/1.black-round.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Pots/c/12867108/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 9, 2, 1, ''),
(44, 'Apple-round', '10', '<b>Apple-round</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Round pots, comfortable for 5 small plant''s.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\nSize : "10 X 10" inch\r\n<br><br>\r\nWeight : 450 gm\r\n<br><br>\r\nPrice : Rs. 325', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/2.Apple-round.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Pots/c/12867108/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 8, 2, 1, ''),
(45, 'Bone Meal Cooked 3', '11', '<b>Bone Meal Cooked 3</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>A wonderful source of organic phosphorus and calcium for all flowering plants, trees and ornamentals, Bone Meal is also recognized as the ideal organic fertilizer when planting bulbs to promote strong root development.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Use Method</b> : 1 Tea-Spoon per 1 Liter-Water\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 500gm \r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 625', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/1.-Bone-Meal-Cooked-3.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/In-organic-Fer/c/12867102/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 3, 2, 1, ''),
(46, 'Flower & Bulb Mix 4', '11', '<b>Flower & Bulb Mix 4</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Flower Mix supplies your favorite bulbs, annuals and perennials with the nutrients they need for vigorous growth and sensational flowering. It is outstanding for roses, blooming bulbs, onions and garlic.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Use Method</b> : 2 Tea-Spoon per 1 Liter-Water\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 500gm \r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 425\r\n', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/2.Flower-Bulb-Mix-4.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/In-organic-Fer/c/12867102/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 2, 2, 1, ''),
(47, 'Maxicrop', '11', '<b>Maxicrop</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>World-famous as a root soak and a foliar-applied plant stimulant. Extracted from fresh Norwegian Ascophyllum kelp, using a process that concentrates all the goodness of the sea into a small amount of material.</p>\r\n<b>Use Method</b> : 2 Tea-Spoon per 1 Liter-Water\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 500gm \r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 725', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/3.Maxicrop.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/In-organic-Fer/c/12867102/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 1, 2, 1, ''),
(48, 'Indian khadh', '11', '<b>Indian khadh</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n <p>Indian khadh is a very useful fertilizer to grow the plant in any season.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Use Method</b> : 1 Tea-Spoon per 1 Liter-Water\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 500 gm\r\n<br><br> \r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 325', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/4.-Indian-khadh.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/In-organic-Fer/c/12867102/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 0, 2, 1, ''),
(49, 'Rose Fertiliser', '12', '<b>Rose Fertiliser</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Specially for rose palnt.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Use Method</b> : 1 Tea-Spoon per 1 Liter-Water\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 500 gm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 550\r\n', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/1.Rose-Fertiliser.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Plant-Specified-Fer/c/12867103/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 4, 2, 1, ''),
(50, 'Planter-fox', '12', '<b>Planter-fox</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Specially for all flower plant of home garden nursery.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Use Method</b> : 2 tablate per liter water\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 500 gm (250 tablate''s)\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 350', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/2.planter-fox.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Plant-Specified-Fer/c/12867103/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 3, 2, 1, ''),
(51, 'Maxi-grow', '12', '<b>Maxi-grow</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Specially for all vegetable product at farm or home garden nursery.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Use Method</b> : 1 Tea-Spoon per 1 Liter-Water\r\n<br>br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 500 gm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 175', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/3.Maxi-grow.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Plant-Specified-Fer/c/12867103/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 2, 2, 1, ''),
(52, 'Dr.earth', '12', '<b>Dr.earth</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Specially for all home based nursery product and also importent for farming sector in agriculture area.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Use Method</b> : 1 Tea-Spoon per 1 Liter-Water \r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight </b>: 500 gm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 450', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/4.Dr_.earth_.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Plant-Specified-Fer/c/12867103/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 1, 2, 1, ''),
(53, 'Gotton-grow', '12', '<b>Cotton-grow</b>\r\n<p>Specially for cotton crops in agriculture sectore.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Use Method</b> : 1 Tea-Spoon per 1 Liter-Water \r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight </b>: 500 gm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 450', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/5.cotton-grow.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Plant-Specified-Fer/c/12867103/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 0, 2, 1, ''),
(54, 'Thrive Alive B-1 - Green Label', '13', '<b>Thrive Alive B-1 - Green Label</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Thrive Alive B-1 stimulates vegetative growth, and will ensure the success of floral crops by promoting flowering during blossoming. Its balanced formulation contains vitamins and nutrients, which are cultured in sea kelp.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Use Method</b>: 20 ml per liter water\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 1 kg\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> :Rs. 1480 ', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/1.Thrive-Alive-B-1-Green-Label.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Liquied-Fer/c/12867106/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 5, 2, 1, ''),
(55, 'Fox Farm Big Bloom', '13', '<b>Fox Farm Big Bloom</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\nRock phosphate helps transfer energy from one part of the plant to another, which means bigger buds and more fragrant flowers.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Use Method</b> : 20 ml per 1 Litter-Water\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 500 gm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 850', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/2.Fox-Farm-Big-Bloom1.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Liquied-Fer/c/12867106/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 3, 2, 1, ''),
(57, 'Indian Kalpwardhan', '13', '<b>Indian Kalpwardhan</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Indian Kalpwardhan is organic in nature and applicable to all types of crops. These extracts are excellent in quality and useful in increasing yield and prolonging shelf life of crops.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Use Method</b> : 20 ml per 1 Liter-Water\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 500 gm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 750', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/3.-Indian-Kalpwardhan.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Liquied-Fer/c/12867106/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 2, 2, 1, ''),
(58, ' Druvex plus', '13', ' <b>Druvex plus</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Druvex plus is organic in nature and applicable to all types of crops. These extracts are excellent in quality and useful in increasing yield and prolonging shelf life of crops.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Use Method</b> : 20 ml per 1 Liter-Water\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b>  : 500 gm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 425', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/4.-Druvex-plus.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Liquied-Fer/c/12867106/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 1, 2, 1, ''),
(59, 'Parker Neem Liquid fertilizer', '13', '<b>Parker Neem Liquid fertilizer</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Parker Neem Liquid fertilizer made out of certified organic ingredients like Neem oil, seaweed (Ascophyllum nodosum) , humic acid, fulvic acid and other natural origin products. NPK 2:2:2.</p>\r\n<br>\r\n<p>Parker Neem Liquid fertilizer has positive effects on plant vitality by promoting vegetative growth and robustness, increases fruit yields and shortens growth cycle. This is due in part to the presence of residual lipid-soluble extracts in Parker Neem Liquid fertilizer that stimulate the intake of micronutrients from the fertilizer and the soil. In some instances, there is even evidence of a shortening in growth cycle.This results in a more robust plant, one that is more tolerant to changes in the environment.<p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Use Method</b> : 50 ml per 1 Liter-Water\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b>  : 1 liter\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 625', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/neem_liquid_fertilizer_up.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Liquied-Fer/c/12867106/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 0, 2, 1, ''),
(60, 'Square-root', '10', '<b>Square-root</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Square pot, comfortable for small size 3 plant''s.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Size</b> : 55 cm X 55 cm\r\n<br><br> \r\n<b>Weight</b> : 380 gm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : 350', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/3.square-root.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Pots/c/12867108/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 7, 2, 1, ''),
(61, 'Tube-green', '10', '<b>Tube-green</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\ndetail :<p>Round pos, Specially for flower plant and bamboo plant</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Size</b> : 35 cm X 35 cm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 1.5 kg\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> :Rs. 850', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/4.tube-green1.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Pots/c/12867108/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 6, 2, 1, ''),
(63, 'Hanging-round', '10', '<b>Hanging-round</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Round pot, specially for more need''d sun light plant.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Size</b> : 25 cm X 25 cm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight-bearing capacity</b> : 3 kg\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 125 gm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 220', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/5.Hanging-round.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Pots/c/12867108/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 5, 2, 1, ''),
(64, 'Rect-suite', '10', 'Rect-suite\r\n<br><br>\r\ndetail :<p> Rectangle pot, Specially for many flower plant''s which include in one pot.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Size</b> : 75 cm X 40 cm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 1250 gm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 560', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/6.rect-suite1.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Pots/c/12867108/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 4, 2, 1, ''),
(65, 'Large-hang', '10', 'Large-hang\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Large size hanging round pot.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Size</b> : 30 cm X 30 cm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight-bearing capacity</b> : 5 kg\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 750 gm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 450', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/7.Large-hang.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Pots/c/12867108/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 3, 2, 1, ''),
(66, 'Hexa-palnt', '10', '<b>Hexa-palnt</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Hexagon pos, use it for any type flower plant.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Size</b> : 30cm X 30cm X 30cm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 550 gm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 250', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/8.Hexa-palnt.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Pots/c/12867108/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 2, 2, 1, ''),
(67, 'Square-tub', '10', '<b>Square-tub</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\ndetail : <p>Square pot, Specially for Single plant.</p>\r\n<b>Size</b> : 20cm X 20cm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 250 gm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 150', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/9.Square-tub.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Pots/c/12867108/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 1, 2, 1, ''),
(68, 'Auto-water', '10', '<b>Auto-water</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Round pot. Specially designed by pot designer for autonomus work to provide water to the plant  regularly according to all plant specification.use it for only single plant.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Size<b> : 20cm X 20cm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight<b> : 750 gm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price<b> : Rs. 850', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/10.Auto-water.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Pots/c/12867108/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 0, 2, 1, ''),
(70, 'Antirrhinum, Snapdragons', '14', '<b>Antirrhinum, Snapdragons</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Season time</b> : Spring\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Antirrhinum is a genus of plants commonly known as snapdragons or dragon flowers</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Height</b> : 3.5 to 6.5 ft\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 675', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/2.Antirrhinum-Snapdragons.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Seasonal-Plants/c/12867096/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 4, 2, 1, ''),
(71, 'Antirrhinum, Snapdragons (Peach)', '14', '<b>Antirrhinum, Snapdragons (Peach)</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Season time</b> : Summer\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Antirrhinum is a genus of plants commonly known as snapdragons or dragon flowers. When all the colors of Antirrhinum are mixed and planted, it gives you a colorful flower bed in your garden. plants are available in plastic pots.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Height</b> : 0.5 to 3.5 ft\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 250', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/3.-Antirrhinum-Snapdragons-Peach.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Seasonal-Plants/c/12867096/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 3, 2, 1, ''),
(72, ' Bleeding Heart ', '14', ' <b>Bleeding Heart</b> \r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Season time</b> : Summer\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p> Bleeding Heart spectabilis is a species of flowering plant in the poppy family Papaveraceae, native to Siberia, northern China, Korea and Japan.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Height</b> : 0.5 to 3.5 ft\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 580', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/4.Bleeding-Heart-summer.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Seasonal-Plants/c/12867096/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 2, 2, 1, ''),
(73, 'Duranta Golden', '14', '<b>Duranta Golden</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Season time</b> : Winter\r\n<br><br> \r\n<p>Duranta erecta is a species of flowering shrub in the verbena family Verbenaceae, ... Common names include golden dewdrop, pigeon berry, and skyflower.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Height</b>: 0.5 to 3.5 ft\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 225\r\n', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/5.duranta-golden.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Seasonal-Plants/c/12867096/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 1, 2, 1, ''),
(74, 'Echinacea Angustifolia', '14', '<b>Echinacea Angustifolia</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Season time</b> : Winter\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Echinacea angustifolia is a herbaceous plant species in Asteraceae. The plants grow 40 to 70 centimetres tall with spindle-shaped taproots that are often branched. The stems and leaves are moderately to densely hairy.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Height</b> : 0.5 to 3.5 ft\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 1050 ', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/6.Echinacea-angustifolia.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Seasonal-Plants/c/12867096/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 0, 2, 1, ''),
(75, 'Aelo Vera', '15', '<b>Aelo Vera</b> \r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Also called Chinese Aloe, Indian Aloe, True Aloe, Barbados Aloe, Burn Aloe, First Aid Plant, Wand of Heaven and Miracle Plant.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Height</b> : 1.0 to 4.5 ft\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 350', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/1.aelo-vera.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Tiny-Plants/c/12867097/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 4, 2, 1, ''),
(76, 'Peperomia (Green Small)', '15', '<b>Peperomia (Green Small)</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n <p>Peperomias are small, easy-care houseplants for low to medium light. Leaves vary in shape and texture from heart-shape to elongated teardrop-shape, and deeply waffled to smooth and waxy.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Height</b> : 0.5 to 2.5 ft\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : RS. 250', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/2.peperomia.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Tiny-Plants/c/12867097/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 3, 2, 1, ''),
(77, 'Paperomia obra', '15', '<b>Paperomia obra</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\ndetail : <p>Peperomias are small, easy-care houseplants for low to medium light. Leaves vary in shape and texture from heart-shape to \r\nelongated teardrop-shape, and deeply waffled to smooth and waxy.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Height</b> : 0.5 to 3.5 ft\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 325', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/3.-paperomia-obra.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Tiny-Plants/c/12867097/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 2, 2, 1, ''),
(78, 'Peperomia Variegated', '15', '<b>Peperomia Variegated</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n <p>Peperomias are small, easy-care houseplants for low to medium light. Leaves vary in shape and texture from heart-shape to elongated teardrop-shape.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Height</b> : 0.5 to 3.5 ft\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 300', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/4.Peperomia-Variegated.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Tiny-Plants/c/12867097/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 1, 2, 1, ''),
(79, 'Sedum Confusum', '15', '<b>Sedum Confusum</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n <p>The fleshy oval dark green leaves concentrate toward the tips of arching branches, forming lush mounds, its used for Container, Groundcover, Hanging Basket, Mixed Border, Rock Garden / Wall.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Height</b> : 0.5 to 3.5 ft\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 325', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/5.Sedum-Confusum.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Tiny-Plants/c/12867097/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 0, 2, 1, ''),
(80, 'Stand-5', '16', '<b>Stand-5</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>This is Three pots stand.Only Three pots are put in to this Stand.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 5 kg\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 500', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/13.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Stands/c/12867085/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 4, 2, 1, ''),
(81, 'Stand-4', '16', '<b>Stand-4</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>This is Five pots stand.Only Five pots are put in to this Stand.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 3 kg\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 250', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/17.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Stands/c/12867085/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 3, 2, 1, ''),
(82, 'Stand-3', '16', '<b>Stand-3</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>This is Five pots stand.Only Five pots are put in to this Stand.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 8 kg\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 650', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/18.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Stands/c/12867085/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 2, 2, 1, ''),
(83, 'Stand-2', '16', '<b>Stand-2</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>This is Three pots stand.Only Three pots are put in to this Stand.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 2 kg\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 150', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/20.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Stands/c/12867085/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 1, 2, 1, ''),
(84, 'Stand-1', '16', '<b>Stand-1</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>This is Table stand.Only Three pots are put in to this Stand.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 5 kg\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 500', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/165086c8d3ac5cc.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Stands/c/12867085/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 0, 2, 1, ''),
(85, 'Nu-Film', '17', '<b>Nu-Film</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Spreader Stickers to Extend Pesticides Superior sticking/extending agent is designed to lengthen the life of foliar-applied insecticides and fungicides.</p>\r\n<br><br> \r\n<b>Use Method</b> : 10 ml per liter water\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 500 gm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : 425', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/1.Nu-Film2.jpg;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Time-Release/c/12867107/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 3, 2, 1, ''),
(86, 'Green gold', '17', '<b>Green gold</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>Green gold is very famous fertilizer in south asia for specially vegetable product of agriculture sectore.\r\nuse method : 1 tea spoon per liter water.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 500 gm\r\n<br><br> \r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 650', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/2.-green-gold.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Time-Release/c/12867107/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 2, 2, 1, ''),
(87, 'G5-bio', '17', '<b>G5-bio</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<p>G5-bio is very famous fertilizer in south india for specially vegetable and flower product of agriculture and farming sectore.</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Use Method</b> : 1 tea spoon per liter water\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b> : 500 gm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 475', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/3.-G5-bio.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Time-Release/c/12867107/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 1, 2, 1, ''),
(88, 'Green-Ayushya', '17', 'Green-Ayushya\r\n<br><br>\r\nGreen-ayushya is very famous fertilizer in all nursery and agriculture product at home garden nursery.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Use Method</b> : 2 tea spoon per liter water.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Weight</b>: 500 gm\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Price</b> : Rs. 250', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/4.green-ayushya.png;', 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=529#!/Time-Release/c/12867107/offset=0&sort=normal', '', '', 0, 2, 1, '');
