(12, 1, '2015-03-03 12:24:31', '2015-03-03 12:24:31', '<h5 style="text-align: justify;"></h5>\r\n<h3><span style="text-decoration: underline; color: #ff6600;">Gift-wrapping ideas</span></h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000;">Presentation can be just as important as the gift itself. Here are some of the decorating ideas we have featured.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000;"><strong>Gift tags:</strong> Make your own gift tags using card in vivid contrasting colours or in tones similar to the flower and pot. Individualise by attaching decorative touches, such as a pretty hairclip, a little peg, a coloured bobby pin or two buttons glued together.</span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000;"><strong>Butterfly and flower tags:</strong> Choose a simple stencil design (available from craft shops) and copy on to coloured or plain card. Make a small hole in the top corner, hook some thin wire through and insert into the soil in your pot. A design on card or balsa wood attached to a bamboo skewer has a similar effect.</span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000;"><strong>Personalised tag:</strong> Paste a photo  of yourself, the two of you together, a shared occasion or interest  on to your tag. You can even make an album, including as many photos as you like.</span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000;"><strong>Flower buttons:</strong> Attach a button to a flower made from card or fabric. Thread ribbon through button and wrap around pot.</span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000;"><strong>Ribbons:</strong> Layer two ribbons of different widths on top of each other, the widest one on the bottom, and wrap around your pot.</span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000;"><strong>Fabric wrap:</strong> Some fabrics, such as tulle or sinamay, have a thick enough weave to be able to stand upright. Finish with a ribbon.</span></li>\r\n</ul>', 'Products', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'products', '', '', '2015-04-20 07:59:31', '2015-04-20 07:59:31', '', 0, 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=12', 0, 'page', '', 0),
