(110, 1, '2015-03-07 11:36:19', '2015-03-07 11:36:19', '<h3 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #ff6600;"><strong><marquee width="100%" bgcolor="#175D36" direction="left" scrollamount="3"> Reasonable Prices.Wide Range of Plants. Attractive Pots &amp; Pot Stands.Only Nursery having Full range of Plants , Pots &amp; Stands.</marquee></strong></span></h3>\r\n<h5 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000;">Plants bring life into all interiors, be it your home or workplace. Plants help to clean the air we breathe and provide peace and tranquility in our often busy lives.</span></h5>\r\n<h5 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000;">Green Gujarat Nursery is a one stop shop for all kinds of plants, pots, exotic wrought iron stands, fertilizers, tools &amp; gardening / landscaping services.</span></h5>\r\n<h5 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000;"> We have a wide range &amp; variety of indoor plants, outdoor plants, trees, palms, creepers &amp; herbal plants.</span></h5>\r\n<h5 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000;">We provide a wide range of planters, pots &amp; hanging baskets made of cement, clay &amp; plastic.</span></h5>\r\n<h5 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000;">We manufacture wrought iron stands to enhance your interiors / exteriors. These stands also help organize your plants / pots in a wonderful fashion.</span></h5>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"></h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #ff6600;"><b>The variety of plants available at our nursery includes :-</b></span></h3>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000;"> flowering shrubs,</span>\r\n<span style="color: #008000;">  palms,</span>\r\n<span style="color: #008000;">  trees,</span>\r\n<span style="color: #008000;">  hanging plants,</span>\r\n<span style="color: #008000;">  ornamental indoor &amp; outdoor plants,</span>\r\n<span style="color: #008000;">  medicinal plants,</span>\r\n<span style="color: #008000;">  landscaping plants,</span>\r\n<span style="color: #008000;">  fruit plants</span>\r\n<span style="color: #008000;">  creepers, etc.</span></h4>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000;"> <span style="color: #ff6600;">Apart from plants, we also deal in :-</span></span></h4>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000; line-height: 1.2;"> plastic, clay &amp; cement pots, planters &amp; hanging baskets</span></h4>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000;">  fertilisers,</span>\r\n<span style="color: #008000;">  garden tools,</span>\r\n<span style="color: #008000;">  exotic wrought iron stands</span>\r\n<span style="color: #008000;">  watering cans, etc.</span></h4>', 'home1', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home1', '', '', '2015-04-12 06:47:58', '2015-04-12 06:47:58', '', 0, 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?page_id=110', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(111, 1, '2015-03-07 11:36:19', '2015-03-07 11:36:19', 'Hey ! Plant Lovers, Now you have a site exclusively for plants. Here you will find lots of information on types of <strong>plants</strong>, how to plant and nurture them, videos, photos and a lot more.\r\n\r\n<strong>Plant life</strong>, the very foundation of our ecosystem is being jeopardized for private and public gain. As a fellow inhabitant, you and me have a responsibility towards other forms of life on this planet. Lets try our best to<strong>preserve Earth''s flora and fauna</strong>.', 'home1', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '110-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-03-07 11:36:19', '2015-03-07 11:36:19', '', 110, 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?p=111', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
