(432, 1, '2015-04-10 13:14:52', '2015-04-10 13:14:52', '<p style="text-align: justify;"></p>\r\n\r\n<h5 style="text-align: justify;"><strong><marquee width="100%" height="80%" bgcolor="#8CEF9E" direction="left">Reasonable Prices.Wide Range of Plants. Attractive Pots &amp; Pot Stands.Only Nursery having Full range of Plants , Pots &amp; Stands.</marquee></strong></h5>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Plants bring life into all interiors, be it your home or workplace. Plants help to clean the air we breathe and provide peace and tranquility in our often busy lives.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Green Gujarat Nursery is a one stop shop for all kinds of plants, pots, exotic wrought iron stands, fertilizers, tools &amp; gardening / landscaping services.\r\nWe have a wide range &amp; variety of indoor plants, outdoor plants, trees, palms, creepers &amp; herbal plants.\r\nWe provide a wide range of planters, pots &amp; hanging baskets made of cement, clay &amp; plastic.\r\nWe manufacture wrought iron stands to enhance your interiors / exteriors. These stands also help organize your plants / pots in a wonderful fashion.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><b>The variety of plants available at our nursery includes</b>\r\n flowering shrubs,\r\n palms,\r\n trees,\r\n hanging plants,\r\n ornamental indoor &amp; outdoor plants,\r\n medicinal plants,\r\n landscaping plants,\r\n fruit plants\r\n creepers, etc.\r\nApart from plants, we also deal in\r\n plastic, clay &amp; cement pots, planters &amp; hanging baskets\r\n fertilisers,\r\n garden tools,\r\n exotic wrought iron stands\r\n watering cans, etc.</p>', 'home1', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '110-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-10 13:14:52', '2015-04-10 13:14:52', '', 110, 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?p=432', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
