(217, 1, '2015-03-10 04:14:46', '2015-03-10 04:14:46', '<h3><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="color: #ff6600; text-decoration: underline;">Seasonal Plants</span></span></h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000;">Tomato, Cucumber and vegetable plants are a speciality here at Belton. We have our own nursery whereby we grow all vegetable plants on the premises. These plants are usually available from March onwards. If planting early you must remember that some vegetable plants do not like cold weather and may need to be in a heated greenhouse!</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000;">Bedding plants and Basket Plants are here in abundance during the spring season, our offering is one of the best in Lincolnshire. All our bedding plants are either grown by ourselves or are selected from specialist British Nurseries  The plants are always of excellent quality.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000;">Hanging baskets and planted containers are planted up by ourselves and are here in abundance throughout the season.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000;">Young plants and seedlings are readily available from February if you wish to grow your own bedding plants on, for your garden tubs and baskets. A great sense of achievement can be had from this approach without the stress of germinating your own seed or rooting cuttings.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000;">Pansies, Violas, Primroses, Polyanthus and Wallflowers are available from September ready for planting after your glorious bedding plants. What a fantastic display these will give throughout the winter.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000;">Planting advice can be offered on colour schemes, types of plants, growing media and containers in this area. Please ask and we will endeavour to Help You!</span></p>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Plants', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '14-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-03-10 04:14:46', '2015-03-10 04:14:46', '', 14, 'http://greengujaratnursery.glocalinfotech.in/?p=217', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(220, 1, '2015-03-10 04:23:55', '2015-03-10 04:23:55', '<h3 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #ff6600;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">In door plants</span></span></h3>\r\n<span style="color: #008000;">Houseplants bring life to your home, not only do they add colour, look good but they also bring a number of health benefits, such as creating a calm and wellbeing to the area, absorb toxins offering cleaner air inside the home, they boost humidity levels and they also dampen noise.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #008000;">A lovely range of seasonal houseplants are stocked at all times.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #008000;">Orchids are a speciality. At Christmas, Poinsettias and Cyclamen are specialities.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #008000;">Houseplants make excellent gifts. We are happy to gift wrap your plant in order to make it extra special.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #008000;">In this department we offer pot covers, fertilizer and compost to enhance the care of your houseplant.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #008000;">If you require assistance with the care of your houseplants please do not hesitate to ask . We have the expertise to offer advise!</span>\r\n<h3><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="color: #ff6600; text-decoration: underline;">Seasonal Plants</span></span></h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000;">Tomato, Cucumber and vegetable plants are a speciality here at Belton. We have our own nursery whereby we grow all vegetable plants on the premises. These plants are usually available from March onwards. If planting early you must remember that some vegetable plants do not like cold weather and may need to be in a heated greenhouse!</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000;">Bedding plants and Basket Plants are here in abundance during the spring season, our offering is one of the best in Lincolnshire. All our bedding plants are